640
00:58:37,628 --> 00:58:40,378
-Yeah?
-Go to where we met the other day.

641
00:58:40,540 --> 00:58:42,427
Walk down the path a little way.

642
00:58:42,588 --> 00:58:45,720
-Why?
-I'll catch up with you this afternoon.

643
00:58:45,884 --> 00:58:49,145
Anybody you call between
now and then is your responsibility.

644
00:59:35,324 --> 00:59:36,698
T om?

645
00:59:42,396 --> 00:59:43,956
Greenleaf?

646
01:00:25,980 --> 01:00:27,867
Quarter past 2.

647
01:00:29,020 --> 01:00:31,224
