for the last two years.

727
01:07:00,572 --> 01:07:03,638
You know what, you're right.
You're absolutely right. It's all my fault.

728
01:07:03,804 --> 01:07:06,586
No. I was a chickenshit.

729
01:07:09,052 --> 01:07:13,176
Ted wanted us to tell you together.
He kept asking, I kept putting it off.

730
01:07:14,012 --> 01:07:16,761
I'll never forget that look
on your face.

731
01:07:16,988 --> 01:07:18,417
Get out! Get out!

732
01:07:19,004 --> 01:07:21,076
-I gotta go.
-Mort, wait. Can't we just--?

733
01:07:21,243 --> 01:07:22,966
No! I've gotta go.

734
01:07:23,131 --> 01:07:25,750
-Will you call me if you need me?
-I doubt it.

735
01:07:25,915 --> 01:07:28,665
-Can I come up there?
-Why on earth would you do that?

736
01:07:29,916 --> 01:07:32,469
You still haven't signed
the papers yet, Mort.

737
01:07:32,987 --> 01:07:35,224
I know you don't want to deal with it.
Me neither.

738
01:07:35,388 --> 01:07:38,137
But everything's been negotiated.
We don't disagree on a thing.

739
01:07:38,300 --> 01:07:41,463
I don't understand why you won't sign.
Don't you want to get it over with?

740
01:07:41,627 --> 01:07:43,122
Unbelievable.

741
01:07:43,868 --> 01:07:46,519
You were worried about me,
and I believed you.

742
01:07:46,683 --> 01:07:48,691
-What an idiot.
-I am worried.

743
01:07:48,860 --> 01:07:52,820
You sound like you did six months
ago, and I think it's my fault.

744
01:07:52,987 --> 01:07:56,184
It's my fault, and I wish
I could take it back, but I can't.

745
01:07:56,348 --> 01:07:58,235
I guess you shouldn't have
fucked him, then!

746
01:08:09,628 --> 01:08:11,002
You're not going up there?

747
01:08:11,163 --> 01:08:13,530
I am not going to
dance around this anymore.

748
01:08:13,691 --> 01:08:17,520
Once he signs, it'll be over. We won't
have these horrible conversations.

749
01:08:17,691 --> 01:08:19,349
All right, well, I'm going with you.

750
01:08:19,515 --> 01:08:23,410
I just.... I really think
I should go alone, Ted.

751
01:08:23,580 --> 01:08:25,303
Well, that makes no sense.

752
01:08:25,467 --> 01:08:27,704
Just the sight of you
is gonna send him.

753
01:08:27,868 --> 01:08:30,737
I was married to the guy for 1 0 years,
I know how to talk to him.

754
01:08:30,908 --> 01:08:33,242
All I want is for this to be over.

755
01:08:34,044 --> 01:08:35,604
Excuse me.

756
01:08:36,412 --> 01:08:38,583
I'll be back around 7.

757
01:08:53,403 --> 01:08:54,865
Hey, Mr. Rainey!

758
01:08:55,035 --> 01:08:56,693
-I'd like to--
-Yeah, yeah, yeah.

759
01:09:02,203 --> 01:09:03,894
Hey. Mr. Rainey.

760
01:09:06,684 --> 01:09:08,539
Mr. Rainey, are you all right?

761
01:09:08,860 --> 01:09:11,794
I'm sorry, my throat just
double-clutched on me for a second.

762
01:09:11,963 --> 01:09:14,200
-You're very pale.
-Yeah, thank you.

763
01:09:14,364 --> 01:09:17,680
Did the UPS guy
drop anything off for me?

764
01:09:19,004 --> 01:09:21,338
-Just the one thing.
-Pardon me?

765
01:09:22,459 --> 01:09:23,703
Just the one thing, I said.

766
01:09:23,868 --> 01:09:25,940
-Oh. Yeah. Thank you.
-Welcome.

767
01:09:26,107 --> 01:09:29,424
Post office would have a cow if they
knew we handled the UPS guy's stuff.

768
01:09:29,595 --> 01:09:32,312
I know that,
and I certainly appreciate it.

769
01:09:32,700 --> 01:09:34,423
You won't tell them, will you?

770
01:09:35,036 --> 01:09:36,891
-No way.
-Good.

771
01:09:37,627 --> 01:09:39,602
Because I saw what you did.

772
01:09:45,115 --> 01:09:47,384
-I'm sorry?
-I said, they'd shoot me if you did.

773
01:09:48,795 --> 01:09:51,097
You ought to go home and lie down,
Mr. Rainey.

774
01:09:51,292 --> 01:09:52,502
You don't look well at all.

775
01:09:53,116 --> 01:09:56,182
Yeah, that's.... That's a good idea.

776
01:10:00,667 --> 01:10:01,845
Cute.

777
01:10:17,755 --> 01:10:20,657
-Got a minute?
-Well, no. I really don't right now.

778
01:10:20,827 --> 01:10:22,802
But I'll give you a call later.

779
01:10:24,315 --> 01:10:26,257
Okay. Sure.

780
01:10:31,643 --> 01:10:33,945
I'm gonna call you
on the phone, okay?

781
