Hi.

922
01:25:18,747 --> 01:25:20,634
-Braces.
-Yeah.

923
01:25:20,794 --> 01:25:22,834
Getting a few things
straightened out.

924
01:25:27,514 --> 01:25:32,336
I was kind of wondering if sometime
you might possibly be interested in--

925
01:25:32,507 --> 01:25:34,547
I don't need a bag.

926
01:26:03,579 --> 01:26:05,237
Mr. Rainey?

927
01:26:07,290 --> 01:26:09,908
Your front door's open.
I'm coming in.

928
01:26:33,818 --> 01:26:35,379
Mr. Rainey?

929
01:26:36,634 --> 01:26:39,634
-Mort Rainey?
-Oh, hi, Dave.

930
01:26:40,698 --> 01:26:42,640
I didn't hear you.
Come on up.

931
01:26:45,530 --> 01:26:47,603
Glad you're here.
I could use the break.

932
01:26:47,770 --> 01:26:50,323
Working lunch. I'm on a roll.

933
01:26:52,731 --> 01:26:53,974
Yeah.

934
01:26:55,578 --> 01:26:57,203
Both you and I know what you did.

935
01:26:59,226 --> 01:27:02,096
Maybe we don't have enough to
put you away now, but eventually...

936
01:27:02,970 --> 01:27:04,880
...we'll find those bodies.

937
01:27:05,050 --> 01:27:06,545
We'll tie you to them...

938
01:27:06,714 --> 01:27:08,340
...and you're going away.

939
01:27:10,011 --> 01:27:13,523
In the meantime, I'd appreciate it if
you didn't come into town anymore.

940
01:27:14,811 --> 01:27:16,337
Makes people uncomfortable.

941
01:27:19,098 --> 01:27:21,465
You can do your shopping
in New London.

942
01:27:23,738 --> 01:27:25,778
Did you hear what I said?

943
01:27:28,186 --> 01:27:30,772
Sure. No problem.

944
01:27:32,378 --> 01:27:33,785
You know...

945
01:27:34,523 --> 01:27:38,134
